{"tid":2201642,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭錦滿：鼓吹「除罩相認，煲底見」嘅人，會害死人。","createTime":"2020-09-14T03:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T18:08:24.000Z","uid":271829,"like":7,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ed995d446c0487cb963fccc332ea557c40ca03af","tid":2201642,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1p6NoOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1p6NoOA.jpg&h=62499dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n鄭錦滿：<br />\n好多人睇完《V煞》電影，只知其然，而不知其所以然，所以有人會認為要仿效結局，「#除罩相認，#煲底見」，因為「#畫面好靚」。<br />\n如果你有認真睇戲了解劇情，就知道最後除低面具影大頭 shot 嘅，都係已經死去嘅角色。鼓吹「除罩相認，煲底見」嘅人，會害死人。<br />\n有人甚至冇睇過電影、小說或者漫畫，就戴住V煞面具跪喺差佬面前舉標語，直頭係對「V煞」呢個符號嘅侮辱。"},{"pid":"1df1b5d184b1f180576c880710a48946e1aa334b","tid":2201642,"uid":3405,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:18:50.000Z","msg":"鼓吹去圖書館直頭戇鳩添啦"},{"pid":"19855b1c7cd81b6bd666b6fa7ca80ae6ebd2d375","tid":2201642,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:18:59.000Z","msg":"jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67bab514e2f58cc376aa8a2051e285e1dbaf45f","tid":2201642,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:22:23.000Z","msg":"四方過四方西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04fffcacbe521498722c8c28c8f5195bffd526b","tid":2201642,"uid":291465,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:22:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uq0a53O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuq0a53O.jpg&h=b0b8d627&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7e000e00050f1478d47fc49cecffc27d6977852e","tid":2201642,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"d67bab514e2f58cc376aa8a2051e285e1dbaf45f","tid":2201642,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:22:23.000Z",